    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A sphere of negative energy ripples out in a 60-foot-radius sphere from a point within range. Each creature in that area must make a Constitution saving throw. A target takes [[/damage 8d6 type=necrotic]] damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/damage 2d6]] for each slot level above 6th.</p></div></div>",
